Usage: read_parasitics [-help] [-force] [-idx] [-idx_spef_type <string>]
                       [-starN] [-via_variation_file <string>] { [{{ [-rc_corner <string>] }} ] }

-help                            # Prints out the command usage
-force                           # Allow block-level to have RCDB or SPEF
                                 # missing for a corner (bool, optional)
-idx                             # Enables the idx flow (bool, optional)
-idx_spef_type <string>          # specifies the type of spef file like idx,
                                 # vidx etc (string, optional)
-rc_corner <string>              # Corner name followed by list of corner
                                 # specific RCDB or SPEF (string, optional)
-starN                           # Specifies whether or not to read the *N
                                 # statements in the SPEF file (bool, optional)
-via_variation_file <string>     # VIA Variation File (string, optional)